        "text": "Procedural World Generation"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Far Cry 6's Yara is a massive open world spanning jungles, beaches, cliffs, and volcanic terrain. I built the procedural pipeline that scatters foliage, generates road and river networks, and blends materials to keep the world believable at AAA scale."
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "World Map Overview"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "The generator outputs biome-aware distribution maps that drive scattering rules per region."
